Mg_sharks
=================
A New Mini Game map!!! 
The Ts control 2 big sharks and they must try to kill the cts with the shark...
The CTs have to kill the little red-white stones in the water... 
After all Stones are destroyed the CTs have won the match. 
Have a lot of fun! :D
=================
